'''征服沙姆陣線'''（Jabhat Fateh al-Sham，{{lang-ar|جبهة فتح الشام}}），原名'''努斯拉陣線'''（al-Nusra Front，{{lang-ar|جبهة النصرة لأهل الشام}}，中文报章和联合国多误译为“叙利亚人民胜利阵线”，部分中文媒体称为“胜利阵线”，正确意译应为“支援阵线”<ref>{{cite web|title=安理会将“叙利亚胜利阵线”列入恐怖组织名单|url=http://news.163.com/13/0601/17/90A3UJ4V00014JB6.html|access-date=2015-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402152745/http://news.163.com/13/0601/17/90A3UJ4V00014JB6.html|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>），原是[[基地組織|基地組織]]在[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/afp/131108/zawahiri-disbands-main-qaeda-faction-syria-0 |title=Zawahiri disbands main Qaeda faction in Syria |publisher=GlobalPost |date=8 November 2013 |accessdate=15 November 2013 |archive-date=2013-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109005944/http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/afp/131108/zawahiri-disbands-main-qaeda-faction-syria-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-01-21/suicide-bomber-hits-hezbollah-stronghold-in-beirut-lebanon/5211872 Al Qaeda-linked group Al Nusra Front claims deadly car bombing in Lebanese capital Beirut] {{Wayback|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-01-21/suicide-bomber-hits-hezbollah-stronghold-in-beirut-lebanon/5211872 |date=20200427063025 }}, ABC, 21 January 2014</ref>的分支。2016年7月28日，努斯拉陣線宣佈改名並脫離基地組織<ref name="bbc160728" />。

[[敘利亞內戰|敘利亞內戰]]開始後，該組織於2012年1月23日宣佈成立<ref name=alarabiya>{{cite news |title=Islamist group claims Syria bombs 'to avenge Sunnis' |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/03/21/202177.html |publisher=[[Al_Arabiya|Al Arabiya]] |date=21 March 2012 |accessdate=23 March 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323034700/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/03/21/202177.html |archivedate=2012年3月23日 |df= }}</ref>，並成為內戰中一支強大的參戰力量。該組織已被[[聯合國|聯合國]]<ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.aljazeera.com/news/americas/2013/05/201353021594299298.html |title = UN blacklists Syria's al-Nusra Front |date = 31 May 2013 |accessdate = 11 June 2013 |publisher = Al Jazeera |archive-date = 2019-05-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190524060715/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/americas/2013/05/201353021594299298.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>、澳大利亞<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-06-29/australia-lists-syrian-group-as-terrorist-organisation/4789476 |title=Australian Government lists anti-Assad Syrian group as terrorist organisation - ABC News (Australian Broadcasting Corporation) |publisher=Australian Broadcasting Corporation |date=29 June 2013 |accessdate=15 November 2013 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003025452/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-06-29/australia-lists-syrian-group-as-terrorist-organisation/4789476 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、加拿大、新西蘭<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.police.govt.nz/sites/default/files/publications/designated-entities-26-11-2014.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-03-06 |archive-date=2018-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007225416/http://www.police.govt.nz/sites/default/files/publications/designated-entities-26-11-2014.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>、俄羅斯<ref name="Russian News Agency TASS">{{cite web |url = http://tass.ru/en/world/769912 |title = Russia calls on all states to put Islamic State, Jabhat al-Nusra on terrorist lists |agency = Russian News Agency "TASS" |accessdate = 29 December 2014 |archive-date = 2016-05-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160529034500/http://tass.ru/en/world/769912 |dead-url = no }}</ref>、英國<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2013/07/19/britain-bans-syria-al-qaida-linked-nusra-front-on-terrorism-grounds/|title=Britain bans Syria's al-Qaida-linked Nusra Front on terrorism grounds|publisher=Fox News Channel|date=19 July 2013|accessdate=15 November 2013|archive-date=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721100604/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2013/07/19/britain-bans-syria-al-qaida-linked-nusra-front-on-terrorism-grounds/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、美國<ref>{{cite news|title=US blacklists Syrian rebel group al-Nusra|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/12/2012121117048117723.html|publisher=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]|date=11 December 2012|accessdate=11 December 2012|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920073320/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/12/2012121117048117723.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和土耳其<ref>{{cite news|title=Turkey lists al-Nusra Front as terrorist organization|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/turkey-lists-al-nusra-front-as-terrorist-organization.aspx?pageID=238&nid=67322|accessdate=3 June 2014|newspaper=Hürriyet Daily News|date=3 June 2014|archive-date=2015-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151103234320/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/turkey-lists-al-nusra-front-as-terrorist-organization.aspx?pageID=238&nid=67322|dead-url=no}}</ref>認定為[[恐怖組織|恐怖組織]]。

